\begin_layout Abstract
This project provides a Liferay portlet with the basic structure to create
 step based web applications.
 It will be the base for a Rapid Assessment for Markets web application
 which will help humanitarian workers to conduct market assessments in order
 to better assist disaster affected populations.
 The development has been carried out following modern software methodologies
 which provide a development and testing framework to ease further development
 and to ensure software quality objectives achievement.
