\begin_layout Standard
The core of new step structure must follow the general structure designed
 for all the portlet, that is to say a symmetric structure comprised of
 the step definition part and the step instance part:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The
\series bold
 step definition 
\series default
regards all those options and configurations defined when creating the tool
 and including the step, namely in the 
\family typewriter
tool-definition
\family default
 portlet created in the 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "subsec:Sixth-Sprint"

\end_inset

